channel.title: A few problems
channel.description:
Well, first off, when I try loading the Downloadable client, it seems to go a bit slow, I've tried multiple Download clients, they all do same thing. I thought this might just be my computer or new java update. It also is laggy, every 5 seconds it lags. ^ That I can deal with.
But, when I try for Exions client (the one with soulsplit :D ). I log on, then get disconnected and keeps happening. Will post a screenie in a bit. Also, in the Log (I Don't Know if thats what its actually called, but I call it that, its the black thing that says everything you do) it says I need to insert my IP address. I right clicked under client.java and found where it said "your ip here", I put in my IP and it still said the same message, I'll also put screenshots here.
2nd Problem [u][b]FIXED[/b][/u], I'm still lagging though. [img]http://img231.imageshack.us/img231/7898/helpem.png[/img] Thanks if you can help me.
